by small shops in every town. look for the characters 复印 (fùyìn) meaning "photocopy" and you will likely be able to get the service you need. printing costs about ¥2 per page and photocopies are ¥0.5 per page. these shops may or may not have internet access so bring your materials on a flash drive. if you are in a university area, there are usually several printing/photocopy shops scattered around the surrounding areas or even within the university. for example, at chongqing jioatong daxue (chongqing transportation university) in nan'an, chongqing, there are at least 11 printshops in various locations around 